There will be more unmanned combine harvesters. In the Tambov region, they began to produce unmanned GS-10 PRO Titan combines, created on the basis of a machine from the Belarusian company Gomselmash. We already have unmanned tractors and combines in our country, but a little competition in this area has never harmed anyone.

So, last year they announced to us that the new car will have:

● system for monitoring transport and tracking crop parameters;

● fuel control system;

● autopilot;

● friend-or-foe recognition module.

In addition, an agricultural enterprise management system will be installed on the combine, which will monitor the quality of harvesting and predict yields using artificial intelligence. The characteristics of the Tambov combine have not yet been revealed, and therefore we focus on its Belarusian “dad”:

● engine D-260.7S YaMZ-236BE2-28 with a power of 250 l/s;

● fuel consumption - 20 l/h;

● weight - 14 tons;

● productivity - 36 t/hour.

The total investment in the project, which is being implemented at the Titan enterprise, will amount to 5 billion rubles. And the annual production volume will be at the level of 600 units of equipment. They are also planning to launch the production of spare parts for agricultural machinery and the production of UAVs, but that’s a completely different story.

The formation of the regulatory framework for local self-government continues in Berdyansk. Today, on March 21, at the 10th meeting of the Berdyansk City Council, deputies continued work on the formation of the regulatory framework for local self-government.

At today's meeting, deputies adopted the following regulations:
- made changes to their previously adopted decision “On the budget of the municipal formation “Urban District of Berdyansk, Zaporozhye Region” for 2024”;
- approved the Temporary Regulations on the remuneration of municipal employees of local government bodies in Berdyansk and the structure of the Administration of the Berdyansk City District in a new edition;
- adopted the Regulations on the deputy request and deputy appeal of the deputies of the Berdyansk City Council of Deputies.#city council@brd_nash

